ry Hee Yong Kai]]<br>{{flagicon|SIN}} [[Loh Kean Hean]]\n| align=\"left\"|21\u201313, 16\u201321, 19\u201321\n| style=\"text-align:left; background:white\"|{{silver2}} '''Runner-up'''\n|}\n:{{Color box|#D8CEF6|border=darkgray}} [[BWF International Challenge]] tournament\n:{{Color box|#E9E9E9|border=darkgray}} [[BWF International Series]] tournament\n\n== Performance timeline ==\n=== Indonesian team ===\n* ''Senior level''\n{| style='font-size: 90%; text-align:center;' class='wikitable'\n! width=180 | Team Events !! [[Badminton at the 2017 Southeast Asian Games|2017]]\n|- style=\"height: 30px;\"\n| bgcolor=ECF2FF style=\"width: 240px;align=left\" | '''[[Southeast Asian Games]]\n| style=\"width: 60px\" |[[File:Med 1.png|Gold]] [[Badminton at the 2017 Southeast Asian Games \u2013 Men's team|Gold]]\n|}\n\n=== Individual competitions ===\n* ''Senior level''\n{| style='font-size: 90%; text-align:center;' class='wikitable'\n|-\n! Event !! 2018\n|- style=\"height: 30px;\"\n| bgcolor=FFAAAA style=\"width: 240px;align=left\" | '''[[Badminton Asia Championships|Asia Championships]]\n| bgcolor=AFEEEE style=\"width: 60px\" |[[2018 Badminton Asia Championships|R2]]\n|}\n{| style='font-size: 90%; text-align:center;' class='wikitable'\n|-\n! Event !! [[2018 BWF World Championships|2018]] !! [[2019 BWF World Championships|2019]]\n|- style=\"height: 30px;\"\n| bgcolor=FFAAAA style=\"width: 240px;align=left\" | '''[[BWF World Championships]]\n| bgcolor=AFEEEE style=\"width: 60px\" |[[2018 BWF World Championships \u2013 Men's doubles|'''R3''']]\n| bgcolor=AFEEEE style=\"width: 60px\" |[[2019 BWF World Championships \u2013 Men's doubles|R2]]\n|}\n{| style='font-size: 90%; text-align:center;' class='wikitable'\n! width=180 | Tournament !! [[2018 BWF World Tour|2018]] !! [[2019 BWF World Tour|2019]] !! Best\n|- bgcolor=DAA520\n| colspan=20 align=center | '''[[BWF World Tour]]\n|-\n|-bgcolor=#C7F2D5\n| align=left | {{flagicon|THA}} [[Thailand Masters (badminton)|Thailand Masters]]\n| bgcol