rl]]\n| Harland Cooper\n| Episode \"[[New Girl (season 4)#ep83|LAXmas]]\"\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation]]\n| Collin Winthrop\n| Episode \"[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation (season 15)#ep335|The End Game]]\"\n|-\n| 2016\u20132017\n| ''[[Still the King (TV series)|Still the King]]''\n| Coy Phisher\n| Recurring role, 9 episodes\n|-\n| 2016\u20132018\n|''[[Girlfriends' Guide to Divorce]]''\n| George McCarthy\n| Recurring role, 6 episodes\n|-\n| 2017\n|''[[The Great Indoors (TV series)|The Great Indoors]]''\n| Mather\n| Episode \"[[The Great Indoors (TV series)#ep10|The Explorers' Club]]\"\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Milo Murphy's Law]]''\n| Clyde Rickenbacker\n| Episodes \"A Clockwork Origin\" and \"The Ticking Clock\"\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[American Housewife]]''\n|Thomas Otto\n|Episode: \"Family Secrets\"<ref>{{cite web|title=AMERICAN HOUSEWIFE: FAMILY SECRETS (11/15)|url=http://www.disneyabcpress.com/abc/pressrelease/american-housewife-family-secrets-1115/|website=disneyabcpress.com|publisher=Disney ABC Television|accessdate=24 November 2017|date=October 30, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201031630/http://www.disneyabcpress.com/abc/pressrelease/american-housewife-family-secrets-1115/|archive-date=1 December 2017|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''Signed, Sealed, Delivered: Home Again''\n| Bill Haywith\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Tangled: The Series]]''\n| Doctor St. Croix\n| Voice role, episode \"Great Expotations\"\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''Christmas in Mississippi''\n| Mr. Kriss\n| Television film (Lifetime)\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Will & Grace]]''\n| Professor Jerry Wise\n| Episode \"Three Wise Men\"\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''Signed, Sealed, Delivered: To the Altar''\n| Bill Haywith\n| Television film\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''Christmas in Louisiana''\n| Timothy Winter\n| Television film (Lifetime)\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Lego The Incredibles]]''\n| Mayor\n| Voice role\n|}\n\n