k |year=2002 |title=Cuban Fire: The Story of salsa and Latin jazz}}\n* {{cite book |last=Maule\u00f3n |first=Rebeca |year=1993 |title=Salsa: Guidebook for Piano and Ensemble |location=Petaluma, California |publisher=Sher Music}}\n* {{cite book |last=Maule\u00f3n |first=Rebeca |title=101 Montunos |location=Petaluma, California |publisher=Sher Music |year=2005 |isbn=978-1-883217-07-5}}\n* {{cite book |last=Manuel |first=Peter |title=Popular Musics of the Non-Western World: an introductory survey |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ou7UQpV1KtwC |publisher=Oxford University Press |isbn=978-0-19-506334-9 |year=1990}}\n* {{cite book |last=Manuel |first=Peter |title=Caribbean Currents: Caribbean Music from Rumba to Reggae |publisher=Temple University Press |location=Philadelphia |isbn=978-1-56639-338-6 |year=1995 |url=https://archive.org/details/caribbeancurrent00manu }}\n* {{cite book |last=Manuel |first=Peter |title=Caribbean Currents: Caribbean Music from Rumba to Reggae |edition=2 |publisher=Temple University Press |location=Philadelphia |year=2006 |isbn=978-1-59213-463-2 |url-access=registration |url=https://archive.org/details/caribbeancurrents00manuel }}\n* {{cite book |last=Morales |first=Ed |title=The Latin Beat |publisher=Da Capo Press |year=2003 |isbn=978-0-306-81018-3 |url=https://archive.org/details/latinbeatrhythms00mora_0 }}\n* Moore, Kevin 2010. ''Beyond Salsa Piano; The Cuban Timba Revolution. v. 1 The Roots of the Piano Tumbao''. Santa Cruz, CA: Moore Music/Timba.com. {{ISBN|978-1-4392-6584-0}}.\n* Moore, Kevin 2010. ''Beyond Salsa Piano; The Cuban Timba Revolution. v. 3 Cuban Piano Tumbaos (1960-1979)''. Santa Cruz, CA: Moore Music/Timba.com. {{ISBN|145054553X}}\n* Moore, Kevin 2011 p.&nbsp;73. ''Beyond Salsa Piano v. 11. C\u00e9sar \"Pupy\" Pedroso: The Music of Los Van Van,'' Part 2. Santa Cruz, CA: Moore Music/Timba.com.{{ISBN|1460965426}}\n* Moore, Kevin 2011. ''Understanding Clave and Clave Changes''. Santa Cruz, CA: Moore Music/Timba.com. {{ISBN